231
00:24:39,680 --> 00:24:41,520
Once it’s done, I go back.

232
00:24:42,640 --> 00:24:44,240
Back to where?

233
00:24:44,640 --> 00:24:46,600
Aren’t we moving in together?

234
00:24:46,640 --> 00:24:49,000
