240
00:25:14,200 --> 00:25:15,720
I like you.

241
00:25:16,200 --> 00:25:18,240
And right now, I really like you too.

242
00:25:19,280 --> 00:25:23,520
Even if I don’t have some special sense
or power to read minds—

243
00:25:23,560 --> 00:25:26,120
